source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000010_OSCHON<tab>The will of the star has entrusted the future to you and yours.
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000010_OSCHON<tab>星の意志は  今の人に未来を託した――

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000020_OSCHON<tab>As entities charged with ensuring life on Etheirys, we rejoice in this outcome with all our hearts.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000020_OSCHON<tab>アーテリスを補強するシステムとして
その結末を  俺たちがどんなに喜んだことか

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000030_THETWELVE<tab>'Tis time, beloved children. Time to bid farewell to we relics of the past.
target:
TEXT_VOICEMAN_06501_000030_THETWELVE<tab>愛しき人の子ら――
どうか旧き人の欠片に  はなむけを――
